  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Was reviewing the deposit contract to see if anything popped out at me and noticed the following lines which seemed strange:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/2e3fcc16f19463bf2e6a95f30489ba51b6aba174/deposit_contract/contracts/validator_registration.vy#L52-L54\r\n\r\nI believe it makes sense in context, but considering it departs from most normal formulations of the algorithm, it should probably have a link to documentation that supports the modified structure for others to reference.",
