    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This is a specific construction used to save gas. Because it is a binary merkle tree filled with 0s to start and leaves only added sequentially, we can use an incremental algorithm that greatly saves gas.\r\n\r\nThere is a formalization/discussion of the algorithm here\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/runtimeverification/verified-smart-contracts/blob/master/deposit/formal-incremental-merkle-tree-algorithm.pdf\r\n\r\nOnce the entirety of the formal work done on the contract is published in the next couple of weeks, we will add links to it all in the repo",
